  id: 1
  title: Assertiveness
  conversationText: 'Marcus: Can you cover my shift Saturday?

    Priya: I might
    have plans already.

    Marcus: I told my boss you''d do it.

    Priya: You
    told them without asking me?

    Marcus: You never have anything going on.'
